Appendix A

referred to in Chapter 1, points 4 and 5 of Annex XII [*]

List as provided by Poland in one language of pharmaceutical products for which a marketing authorisation issued under Polish law prior to the date of accession shall remain valid until it is renewed in compliance with the acquis or until 31 December 2008, whichever is the earlier.

Mention on this list does not prejudge whether or not the pharmaceutical product in question has a marketing authorisation in compliance with the acquis.
